 Let $A = \begin{pmatrix} 5 \\ 0 \end{pmatrix}$ and $B = \begin{pmatrix} 4 \\ 3 \end{pmatrix}.$  Let $P$ be the point $\begin{pmatrix} -2 \\ 3 \end{pmatrix},$ and let $Q$ be its reflection across line $AB.$

[asy]
